des: This skill supports binding your smart home devices and provides voice interactive operation. Currently supported devices: webcams, supported functions: watch cameras on echo show, and will support more smart home devices and functions in the future. You need to download the VeeSee app, You can start using this skill after creating an account in VeeSee.
